<div class="cover w-100 text-primary overflow-hidden m-0 p-0 position-relative ">
    <h2 class="fw-bold text-white fs-1 position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle text-uppercase" style="letter-spacing: 1rem;">{{title}}</h2>
    <img class="title" style="margin-top: -20%" src="/img/descarga.jpg" alt="">
</div>
<div class="bg-white mb-0">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-7 p-5">
          <div class="row ">
            <div class="col text-center section">
              <h2
								class="display-4 font-weight-normal"
							>Correo</h2>
              <hr size="6" width="80%" style="margin: 0 auto;" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row pt-3 block">
            <div class="col">
              <h5>Contáctanos a través del siguiente formulario para hacernos llegar un correo sobre el asunto, aclaración o duda que tengas</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
          <form class="contact mt-2 block" action="/send-email">
            <div class="row contact">
              <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="input-group mb-3">
                  <span class="input-group-text"><i class="fas fa-user fa-lg"></i></span>
                  <div class="has-float-label">
                    <input class="form-control" id="name" type="text" placeholder=""/>
                    <label for="name">Nombre</label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="input-group mb-3">
                  <span class="input-group-text"><i class="fas fa-phone-alt fa-lg"></i></span>
                  <div class="has-float-label">
                    <input class="form-control" id="tel" type="tel" placeholder=""/>
                    <label for="tel">Teléfono</label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="input-group mb-3">
                  <span class="input-group-text"><i class="fas fa-book-open "></i></span>
                  <div class="has-float-label">
                    <input class="form-control" id="asunto" type="text" placeholder=""/>
                    <label for="asunto">Asunto</label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="input-group mb-3">
                  <span class="input-group-text"><i class="fas fa-envelope fa-lg"></i></span>
                  <div class="has-float-label">
                    <input class="form-control" id="email" type="email" placeholder=""/>
                    <label for="email">Correo</label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col">
                <div class="input-group mb-3">
                  <span class="input-group-text"><i class="fas fa-file-alt fa-lg"></i></span>
                  <div class="has-float-label">
                    <textarea class="form-control" style="min-height: 5rem; max-height: 10rem;" id="msg" type="text" placeholder=""></textarea>
                    <label for="msg">Mensaje</label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row my-3">
              <div class="d-grid col-md-8 mx-auto gap-2">
                <button class="btn btn-primary send" type="button">Enviar</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 p-5 bg-dark text-white d-flex align-items-center">
            <div>
              <div class="row">
              <div class="col text-center section">
                <h2
								class="display-4 font-weight-normal"
							>Redes sociales</h2>
                <hr size="6" width="80%" style="margin: 0 auto;" />
              </div>
              </div>
              <div class="row pt-3 block">
                <div class="col text-secondary">
                  <h5 style="text-align: center !important;">¡ Encuéntranos a través de nuestras redes sociales para enterarte de todas las novedades de AdsPost !</h5>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="redes block">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 my-4 d-flex justify-content-center align-content-center flex-wrap">
                    <i class="fab fa-facebook-f fs-2"></i>
                    <a href="#" class="my-auto ps-3 fw-light text-decoration-none"><b>@AdsPost-fb</b></a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 my-4 d-flex justify-content-center align-content-center flex-wrap">
                    <i class="fa fa-instagram fs-2"></i>
                    <a href="#" class="my-auto ps-3 fw-light text-decoration-none"><b>@AdsPost-ig</b></i></a>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 my-4 d-flex justify-content-center align-content-center flex-wrap">
                    <i class="fab fa-linkedin fs-2"></i>
                    <a href="#" class="my-auto ps-3 fw-light text-decoration-none"><b>@AdsPost-in</b></a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 my-4 d-flex justify-content-center align-content-center flex-wrap" >
                    <i class="fa fa-envelope fs-2"></i>
                    <a href="#" class="my-auto ps-3 fw-light text-decoration-none"><b>@AdsPost-gm</b></a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

